<p>
<lb n="1"/>Āsīdgoṁkkamahīśamātula Ivā śrīpaṁḍadaṁḍādhipastanmaṁtrī <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>vallivāstavyakaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dārākhyā dharaṇīsurōttamajani<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> pratyakṣadharmmātmajō <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <unclear>nā</unclear>mnanāmavibhu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>guṇabhūre<unclear>ṟi</unclear>yāṁbikānaṁddanaḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākābdānāṁ samājē rasagirigaganaścaṁdrasaṁkhyāsamētē dharmma 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>jñassatyasaṁddhassakalaguṇanidhirnnāgadēvassumaṁtrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śriṣṭisthityaṁttakarttrōrvvimalajalanidhau yō
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ganidrēratāya prādāddēvāya dīpaṁjagadadhipatayē bhāvanārāyaṇāya <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tribhu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vanacakravartti śrīrājarājadēvara divyasaṁvatsaraṁbulu 9 di yagu śrāhi śakavarṣaṁbu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>lu 1076 gunēṁṭi phālguṇa śuddha paṁccādaśiyu śanivāramunāṁḍu gōkarāju māma daṁḍanāya
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ka paṁḍanāyakula nāmanapeggaḍa gammanāṁṭi prēṁppalli śrībhāvanārāyaṇadēvara kācaṁdrārkka
<lb n="9"/><unclear>ma</unclear>khaṁḍavartti dīpamunakuṁ beṭṭina birudumāḍalu vaṁḍreṁḍu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vīniṁ jēkoni Iṁdula kā
<lb n="10" break="no"/>pulu madhuvanavaṁḍitula koḍku vermmāḍi Aradiviyayuṁ gāmarāju koḍku nāgadē
<lb n="11" break="no"/>vaṇḍu Aradi<note n="76-1">The letter di is engraved below the line.</note>viyayunuṁ gā niddaṟuṁ gūḍi tama putrānupautrikamu nitya mā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>neṁḍu neyi vōyaṁggalavāru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

